20the%20Kecare%20Generator%20CLI%20for%20you.%5Cn%5Cn%3A%3A%3A%20tabs%5Cn%5Cn%40tab%20npm%5Cn%5Cn%60%60%60bash%5Cnnpm%20create%20kecare%5Cn%60%60%60%5Cn%5Cn%40tab%20bun%5Cn%5Cn%60%60%60bash%5Cnbun%20create%20kecare%5Cn%60%60%60%5Cn%5Cn%40tab%20pnpm%5Cn%5Cn%60%60%60bash%5Cnpnpm%20create%20kecare%5Cn%60%60%60%5Cn%5Cn%3A%3A%3A%5Cn%5CnIf%20everything%20goes%20well%2C%20you%20will%20see%20a%20success%20message.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%20Get%20Theme%20or%20Starter%20Template%5Cn%5Cn%3E%20%5B!NOTE%5D%5Cn%3E%5Cn%3E%20Currently%2C%20Kecare%20is%20still%20in%20its%20early%20stages%2C%20so%20there%20aren't%20many%20themes%20available%20to%20choose%20from.%20We%20appreciate%20everyone's%20contributions%20to%20Kecare%20by%20creating%20themes%20to%20enrich%20the%20ecosystem.%20For%20now%2C%20you%20can%20use%20the%20theme%20we%20provide%20to%20experience%20the%20advantages%20that%20Kecare%20brings.%5Cn%5Cn%60%60%60bash%5Cngit%20clone%20https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FPamperkyumi%2FKecare-theme.git%5Cncd%20Kecare-theme%5Cn%60%60%60%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%20Install%20Dependencies%5Cn%5Cn%3A%3A%3A%20tabs%5Cn%5Cn%40tab%20bun%5Cn%5Cn%60%60%60bash%5Cnbun%20install%5Cn%60%60%60%5Cn%5Cn%40tab%20npm%5Cn%5Cn%60%60%60bash%5Cnnpm%20install%20%5Cn%60%60%60%5Cn%40tab%20pnpm%5Cn%5Cn%60%60%60bash%5Cnpnpm%20install%20%5Cn%60%60%60%5Cn%5Cn%3A%3A%3A%5Cn%5CnIf%20everything%20goes%20smoothly%2C%20you%20will%20receive%20a%20theme%20with%20the%20following%20main%20directory%20structure%2C%5Cn%5Cn%60%60%60%60bash%5Cntheme%2F%5Cn%E2%94%9C%E2%94%80%E2%94%80%20.kecare%2F%5Cn%E2%94%82%20%20%20%E2%94%9C%E2%94%80%E2%94%80%20articles%2F%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%23%20%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95(%E5%B0%86markdown%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%94%BE%E7%BD%AE%E4%BA%8E%E6%AD%A4)%5Cn%E2%94%82%20%20%20%E2%94%82%5Cn%E2%94%82%20%20%20%E2%94%9C%E2%94%80%E2%94%80%20menus%2F%5Cn%E2%94%82%20%20%20%E2%94%82%20%20%20%E2%94%9C%E2%94%80%E2%94%80%20test.menu.source.ts%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%23%20%E8%8F%9C%E5%8D%95%E6